### Get Profile
GET {{host}}/api/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Update Profile
PUT {{host}}/api/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "phone": "0987654321",
    "company": "Tech Corp",
    "job_title": "Developer",
    "bio": "Laravel developer",
    "social_url": "https://linkedin.com/in/johndoe"
}

### Upload Profile Photo
POST {{host}}/api/profile/photo
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="profile.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./profile.jpeg
--WebAppBoundary--

### Get QR Code
GET {{host}}/api/profile/qr-code
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Public Profile
GET {{host}}/api/u/{{qr_hash}}
Accept: application/json
